<p><a name="References" id="References"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=History_of_India&amp;action=edit&amp;section=22" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<div class="noprint tright portal" style="border:solid #aaa 1px;margin:0.5em 0 0.5em 0.5em;">
