<li><a href="/wiki/R.S._Sharma" title="R.S. Sharma" class="mw-redirect">R.S. Sharma</a>, Indo-European languages and historical problems (Symposia papers), <a href="/wiki/Indian_History_Congress" title="Indian History Congress">Indian History Congress</a>, 1994.</li>
